---

<section
  id="como-trabajamos"
  class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-bg to-white"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2
        class="font-bricolage text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-black mb-4"
      >
        ¿Cómo trabajamos?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Un proceso simple y transparente para llevar tu negocio al siguiente
        nivel
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div
              class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-brand-cyan rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg"
            >
              <span class="text-white font-bricolage text-2xl font-bold">1</span
              >
            </div>
            <div
              class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-brand-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-black"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-bricolage text-2xl font-bold text-brand-black mb-4">
            Escuchamos
          </h3>

          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Nos reunimos con vos para entender tus procesos, necesidades y
            objetivos. Queremos conocer tu negocio a fondo.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="hidden md:block absolute top-10 left-full w-full h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-blue to-brand-cyan -translate-x-1/2 z-0"
        >
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div
              class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-cyan to-brand-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg"
            >
              <span class="text-white font-bricolage text-2xl font-bold">2</span
              >
            </div>
            <div
              class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-brand-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-black"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-bricolage text-2xl font-bold text-brand-black mb-4">
            Proponemos
          </h3>

          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Diseñamos una solución a medida con las automatizaciones específicas
            que tu negocio necesita para crecer.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="hidden md:block absolute top-10 left-full w-full h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-cyan to-brand-green -translate-x-1/2 z-0"
        >
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div
              class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-green to-brand-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg"
            >
              <span class="text-white font-bricolage text-2xl font-bold">3</span
              >
            </div>
            <div
              class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-brand-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-black"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-bricolage text-2xl font-bold text-brand-black mb-4">
            Automatizamos
          </h3>

          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Implementamos las soluciones, te capacitamos y te acompañamos en
            cada paso. Tu éxito es nuestro éxito.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <div class="inline-block bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Tiempo promedio de implementación</p>
        <p class="font-bricolage text-4xl font-bold text-brand-blue">
          2-4 semanas
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
